WEBVTT

00:10.010 --> 00:13.579
<i>"They call it</i>
<i>a Valentine, my dear,</i>

00:13.581 --> 00:15.514
<i>"and they tell me</i>
<i>it's all the rage in england</i>

00:15.516 --> 00:17.916
<i>"these days.</i>

00:17.918 --> 00:18.984
<i>"Of course,</i>

00:18.986 --> 00:21.353
<i>"a gentleman like you</i>
<i>has little interest</i>

00:21.355 --> 00:22.521
<i>"in the new styles,</i>

00:22.523 --> 00:25.824
<i>"but if valentines ever</i>
<i>become popular in America,</i>

00:25.826 --> 00:29.461
<i>"then you will likely receive</i>
<i>many of these in your life,</i>

00:29.463 --> 00:33.432
<i>"and I want to give you</i>
<i>your first,</i>

00:33.434 --> 00:35.901
<i>"as it will surely be</i>
<i>the only Valentine,</i>

00:35.903 --> 00:37.903
<i>"and the last,</i>

00:37.905 --> 00:42.141
<i>that I will ever give to you."</i>

