45:57.455 --> 45:59.388
Homelessness
in this country...

46:01.492 --> 46:02.725
...in America...

46:04.461 --> 46:05.461
...is a new concept...

46:05.463 --> 46:07.830
It's...

46:07.832 --> 46:09.832
I mean, it's not...

46:19.376 --> 46:21.477
<i>"I realized two things</i>

46:21.479 --> 46:24.614
<i>"this morning, maddie.</i>

